== Shōshoi == * Located in {{ill|Kamaishi, Iwate|ja|釜石市|qq=draft}}, Iwate Prefecture. Official name: {{ill|Kamaishi Steelworks Mountain Shrine|ja|釜石製鐵所山神社|qq=draft}}. * Located in Uguisuzawa, {{ill|Kurihara, Miyagi|ja|栗原市|qq=draft}}, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Ōme, Kawaminami-shimo, Wakayanagi, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Ōmori, Kamihataoka, Wakayanagi, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Ōzawa, Ichihasama, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Minamisawa, Shimizume, Ichihasama, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Kurikoma, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. Commonly referred to as {{ill|Sakurada Mountain Shrine|ja|櫻田山神社|qq=draft}}. * Located in Ōmuro, Jūsan-hama, Kitakami, {{ill|Ishinomaki, Miyagi|ja|石巻市|qq=draft}}, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Kotaki, Jūsan-hama, Kitakami, Ishinomaki, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Shibata, Miyagi|ja|柴田町|qq=draft}}, Shibata District, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Watari, Miyagi|ja|亘理町|qq=draft}}, Watari District, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Shinjō, Yamagata|ja|新庄市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. There are four such shrines within the city. * Located in {{ill|Kaneyama, Yamagata|ja|金山町|qq=draft}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 12 in the town. * Located in {{ill|Mogami, Yamagata|ja|最上町|qq=draft}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 2 in the town. * Located in {{ill|Funagata, Yamagata|ja|舟形町|qq=draft}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 2 in the town. * Located in {{ill|Mamurogawa, Yamagata|ja|真室川町|qq=draft}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 19 in the town. * Located in {{ill|Sakegawa, Yamagata|ja|鮭川村|qq=draft}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 2 in the village. * Located in {{ill|Tozawa, Yamagata|ja|戸沢村|qq=draft}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 9 in the village. * Located in Ichiriyama Kanayama, {{ill|Kariya, Aichi|ja|刈谷市|qq=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Shirahama, Wakayama|ja|白浜町|qq=draft}}, Nishimuro District, Wakayama Prefecture. * Located in Minase, {{ill|Yamakawa, Tokushima|ja|山川町|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Yoshinogawa, Tokushima|ja|吉野川市|qq=draft}}, Tokushima Prefecture. See also {{ill|Kamizuki Shrine|ja|紙漉神社|qq=draft}}. * Located in Higashino 3-chome, {{ill|Matsuyama, Ehime|ja|松山市|qq=draft}}, Ehime Prefecture.
== Yamajinja == * Located in {{ill|Kitaakita, Akita|ja|北秋田市|qq=draft}}, Akita Prefecture. Former Village shrine. * Located in Mogami, Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations in town. * Located in {{ill|Mikawa, Yamagata|ja|三川町|qq=draft}}, Higashitagawa District, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Yamagata, Yamagata|ja|山形市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations. Additionally, three Mountain God Shrines exist. * Located in {{ill|Sagae, Yamagata|ja|寒河江市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Murayama, Yamagata|ja|村山市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations. * Located in {{ill|Tendō, Yamagata|ja|天童市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Higashine, Yamagata|ja|東根市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in {{ill|Obanazawa, Yamagata|ja|尾花沢市|qq=draft}}, Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in {{ill|Asahi, Yamagata|ja|朝日町|qq=draft}}, Nishimurayama District, Yamagata Prefecture. Another Mountain God Shrine is present. * Located in Ōe, Nishimurayama District, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in {{ill|Shirataka, Yamagata|ja|白鷹町|qq=draft}}, Nishiokitama District, Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in {{ill|Kimitsu, Chiba|ja|君津市|qq=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. Former Village shrine. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Utsunomiya)|ja|山神社 (宇都宮市)|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Utsunomiya, Tochigi|ja|宇都宮市|qq=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture. * Located in Sakura-ga-oka, {{ill|Tama, Tokyo|ja|多摩市|qq=draft}}, Tokyo. * Located in Araya, {{ill|Fujiyoshida, Yamanashi|ja|富士吉田市|qq=draft}}, Yamanashi Prefecture. See also {{ill|Araya Mountain Shrine|ja|新屋山神社|qq=draft}}. * Located in Tashirochō, {{ill|Chikusa-ku, Nagoya|ja|千種区|qq=draft}}, Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Matsubara, {{ill|Naka-ku, Nagoya|ja|中区|qq=draft}}, Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Yasui, {{ill|Kita-ku, Nagoya|ja|北区|qq=draft}}, Nagoya. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Toyooka)|ja|山神社 (豊岡市)|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Toyooka, Hyōgo|ja|豊岡市|qq=draft}}, Hyōgo Prefecture. One of the {{ill|Myōjin Taisha|ja|名神大社|qq=draft}}. * Located in Hagiwara, Matsuyama, Ehime Prefecture. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Shinkamigotō)|ja|山神社 (新上五島町)|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Shinkamigotō, Nagasaki|ja|新上五島町|qq=draft}}, Minamimatsuura District, Nagasaki Prefecture. * Located in Hirouchi, {{ill|Ōita, Ōita|ja|大分市|qq=draft}}, Ōita Prefecture.
== Yama no Kamisha == * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Misato, Miyagi)|ja|山神社 (美里町)|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Misato, Miyagi|ja|美里町|qq=draft}}, Tōda District, Miyagi Prefecture. {{ill|Former Village shrine|ja|旧郷社|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Chūō, Yamanashi)|ja|山神社 (中央市)|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Chūō, Yamanashi|ja|中央市|qq=draft}}, Yamanashi Prefecture. * Located in Chita, {{ill|Minato-ku, Nagoya|ja|港区_(名古屋市)|qq=draft}}, Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Nishimarune, Ōdaka-chō, {{ill|Midori-ku, Nagoya|ja|緑区_(名古屋市)|qq=draft}}, Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Setogawa-chō, {{ill|Owariasahi, Aichi|ja|尾張旭市|qq=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yamano-kami-chō, {{ill|Handa, Aichi|ja|半田市|qq=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. Written as "Yama no Jinja" (山之神社). * Located in Tenno-chō, Handa, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yanabehigashimachi, Handa, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yama no Kami, {{ill|Taketoyo, Aichi|ja|武豊町|qq=draft}}, Chita District, Aichi Prefecture. Written as "Yama no Jinja" (山ノ神社).
In the Tōkai region, most of these are small shrines, but there are a large number overall, especially when including shrine precinct shrines.
== Yamagamisha == * Located in Yamakamichō, {{ill|Hekinan, Aichi|ja|碧南市|qq=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture.
