'''Mountain Shrine''' (山神社) is a [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] in [[:en:Japan|Japan]], located in various places throughout the country.
== Shōshoi == * Located in [[:en:Kamaishi, Iwate|Kamaishi, Iwate]], Iwate Prefecture. Official name: {{ill|Kamaishi Steelworks Mountain Shrine|ja|釜石製鐵所山神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamaishi Steelworks Mountain Shrine|qq=}}. * Located in Uguisuzawa, [[:en:Kurihara, Miyagi|Kurihara, Miyagi]], Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Ōme, Kawaminami-shimo, Wakayanagi, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Ōmori, Kamihataoka, Wakayanagi, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Ōzawa, Ichihasama, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Minamisawa, Shimizume, Ichihasama, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Kurikoma, Kurihara, Miyagi Prefecture. Commonly referred to as {{ill|Sakurada Mountain Shrine|ja|櫻田山神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakurada Mountain Shrine|qq=}}. * Located in Ōmuro, Jūsan-hama, Kitakami, [[:en:Ishinomaki|Ishinomaki, Miyagi]], Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in Kotaki, Jūsan-hama, Kitakami, Ishinomaki, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Shibata, Miyagi|Shibata, Miyagi]], Shibata District, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Watari, Miyagi|Watari, Miyagi]], Watari District, Miyagi Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Shinjō, Yamagata|Shinjō, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. There are four such shrines within the city. * Located in {{ill|Kaneyama, Yamagata|ja|金山町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaneyama, Yamagata|qq=}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 12 in the town. * Located in [[:en:Mogami, Yamagata|Mogami, Yamagata]], Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 2 in the town. * Located in [[:en:Funagata, Yamagata|Funagata, Yamagata]], Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 2 in the town. * Located in [[:en:Mamurogawa|Mamurogawa, Yamagata]], Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 19 in the town. * Located in [[:en:Sakegawa|Sakegawa, Yamagata]], Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 2 in the village. * Located in [[:en:Tozawa, Yamagata|Tozawa, Yamagata]], Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture. There are 9 in the village. * Located in Ichiriyama Kanayama, [[:en:Kariya, Aichi|Kariya, Aichi]], Aichi Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Shirahama, Wakayama|Shirahama, Wakayama]], Nishimuro District, Wakayama Prefecture. * Located in Minase, {{ill|Yamakawa, Tokushima|ja|山川町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamakawa, Tokushima|qq=}}, [[:en:Yoshinogawa, Tokushima|Yoshinogawa, Tokushima]], Tokushima Prefecture. See also {{ill|Kamizuki Shrine|ja|紙漉神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamizuki Shrine|qq=}}. * Located in Higashino 3-chome, [[:en:Matsuyama|Matsuyama, Ehime]], Ehime Prefecture.
== Yamajinja == * Located in [[:en:Kitaakita|Kitaakita, Akita]], Akita Prefecture. Former Village shrine. * Located in Mogami, Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations in town. * Located in [[:en:Mikawa, Yamagata|Mikawa, Yamagata]], Higashitagawa District, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Yamagata (city)|Yamagata, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations. Additionally, three Mountain God Shrines exist. * Located in [[:en:Sagae|Sagae, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Murayama, Yamagata|Murayama, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations. * Located in [[:en:Tendō, Yamagata|Tendō, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Higashine|Higashine, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in [[:en:Obanazawa|Obanazawa, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in {{ill|Asahi, Yamagata|ja|朝日町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Asahi, Yamagata|qq=}}, Nishimurayama District, Yamagata Prefecture. Another Mountain God Shrine is present. * Located in Ōe, Nishimurayama District, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Shirataka|Shirataka, Yamagata]], Nishiokitama District, Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in [[:en:Kimitsu|Kimitsu, Chiba]], Chiba Prefecture. Former Village shrine. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Utsunomiya)|ja|山神社 (宇都宮市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Utsunomiya)|qq=}} – Located in [[:en:Utsunomiya|Utsunomiya, Tochigi]], Tochigi Prefecture. * Located in Sakura-ga-oka, [[:en:Tama, Tokyo|Tama, Tokyo]], Tokyo. * Located in Araya, [[:en:Fujiyoshida|Fujiyoshida, Yamanashi]], Yamanashi Prefecture. See also {{ill|Araya Mountain Shrine|ja|新屋山神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Araya Mountain Shrine|qq=}}. * Located in Tashirochō, [[:en:Chikusa-ku, Nagoya|Chikusa-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Matsubara, [[:en:Central District|Naka-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Yasui, [[:en:北區|Kita-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Toyooka)|ja|山神社 (豊岡市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Toyooka)|qq=}} – Located in [[:en:Toyooka, Hyōgo|Toyooka, Hyōgo]], Hyōgo Prefecture. One of the {{ill|Myōjin Taisha|ja|名神大社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōjin Taisha|qq=}}. * Located in Hagiwara, Matsuyama, Ehime Prefecture. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Shinkamigotō)|ja|山神社 (新上五島町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Shinkamigotō)|qq=}} – Located in [[:en:Shin-Kamigotō|Shinkamigotō, Nagasaki]], Minamimatsuura District, Nagasaki Prefecture. * Located in Hirouchi, [[:en:Ōita (city)|Ōita, Ōita]], Ōita Prefecture.
== Yama no Kamisha == * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Misato, Miyagi)|ja|山神社 (美里町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Misato, Miyagi)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Misato, Miyagi|ja|美里町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Misato, Miyagi|qq=}}, Tōda District, Miyagi Prefecture. {{ill|Former Village shrine|ja|旧郷社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Former Village shrine|qq=}}. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Chūō, Yamanashi)|ja|山神社 (中央市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Chūō, Yamanashi)|qq=}} – Located in [[:en:Chūō, Yamanashi|Chūō, Yamanashi]], Yamanashi Prefecture. * Located in Chita, [[:en:Minato-ku, Nagoya|Minato-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Nishimarune, Ōdaka-chō, [[:en:Midori-ku, Nagoya|Midori-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Setogawa-chō, [[:en:Owariasahi|Owariasahi, Aichi]], Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yamano-kami-chō, [[:en:Handa, Aichi|Handa, Aichi]], Aichi Prefecture. Written as "Yama no Jinja" (山之神社). * Located in Tenno-chō, Handa, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yanabehigashimachi, Handa, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yama no Kami, [[:en:Taketoyo|Taketoyo, Aichi]], Chita District, Aichi Prefecture. Written as "Yama no Jinja" (山ノ神社).
In the Tōkai region, most of these are small shrines, but there are a large number overall, especially when including shrine precinct shrines.
== Yamagamisha == * Located in Yamakamichō, [[:en:Hekinan|Hekinan, Aichi]], Aichi Prefecture.
