== Yamajinja == * Located in [[:en:Kitaakita|Kitaakita, Akita]], Akita Prefecture. Former Village shrine. * Located in Mogami, Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations in town. * Located in [[:en:Mikawa, Yamagata|Mikawa, Yamagata]], Higashitagawa District, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Yamagata (city)|Yamagata, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations. Additionally, three Mountain God Shrines exist. * Located in [[:en:Sagae|Sagae, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Murayama, Yamagata|Murayama, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Two locations. * Located in [[:en:Tendō, Yamagata|Tendō, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Higashine|Higashine, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in [[:en:Obanazawa|Obanazawa, Yamagata]], Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in {{ill|Asahi, Yamagata|ja|朝日町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Asahi, Yamagata|qq=|1=Asahi, Yamagata|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1206007}}, Nishimurayama District, Yamagata Prefecture. Another Mountain God Shrine is present. * Located in Ōe, Nishimurayama District, Yamagata Prefecture. * Located in [[:en:Shirataka|Shirataka, Yamagata]], Nishiokitama District, Yamagata Prefecture. Three locations. * Located in [[:en:Kimitsu|Kimitsu, Chiba]], Chiba Prefecture. Former Village shrine. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Utsunomiya)|ja|山神社 (宇都宮市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Utsunomiya)|qq=|1=Yama Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11470797}} – Located in [[:en:Utsunomiya|Utsunomiya, Tochigi]], Tochigi Prefecture. * Located in Sakura-ga-oka, [[:en:Tama, Tokyo|Tama, Tokyo]], Tokyo. * Located in Araya, [[:en:Fujiyoshida|Fujiyoshida, Yamanashi]], Yamanashi Prefecture. See also {{ill|Araya Mountain Shrine|ja|新屋山神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Araya Mountain Shrine|qq=|1=Araya Yama Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q106388142}}. * Located in Tashirochō, [[:en:Chikusa-ku, Nagoya|Chikusa-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Matsubara, [[:en:Central District|Naka-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Yasui, [[:en:北區|Kita-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Toyooka)|ja|山神社 (豊岡市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Toyooka)|qq=|1=Yama Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q21655261}} – Located in [[:en:Toyooka, Hyōgo|Toyooka, Hyōgo]], Hyōgo Prefecture. One of the {{ill|Myōjin Taisha|ja|名神大社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōjin Taisha|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}. * Located in Hagiwara, Matsuyama, Ehime Prefecture. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Shinkamigotō)|ja|山神社 (新上五島町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Shinkamigotō)|qq=|1=Yama Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11470799}} – Located in [[:en:Shin-Kamigotō|Shinkamigotō, Nagasaki]], Minamimatsuura District, Nagasaki Prefecture. * Located in Hirouchi, [[:en:Ōita (city)|Ōita, Ōita]], Ōita Prefecture.
== Yama no Kamisha == * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Misato, Miyagi)|ja|山神社 (美里町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Misato, Miyagi)|qq=|1=Yama-no-Kami Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q17224192}} – Located in {{ill|Misato, Miyagi|ja|美里町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Misato, Miyagi|qq=|1=Misato, Miyagi|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11609412}}, Tōda District, Miyagi Prefecture. {{ill|Former Village shrine|ja|旧郷社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Former Village shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度|1=modern system of ranked Shinto shrines|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q712534}}. * {{ill|Mountain Shrine (Chūō, Yamanashi)|ja|山神社 (中央市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mountain Shrine (Chūō, Yamanashi)|qq=|1=Yama Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q22120748}} – Located in [[:en:Chūō, Yamanashi|Chūō, Yamanashi]], Yamanashi Prefecture. * Located in Chita, [[:en:Minato-ku, Nagoya|Minato-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Nishimarune, Ōdaka-chō, [[:en:Midori-ku, Nagoya|Midori-ku, Nagoya]], Nagoya. Former Village shrine. * Located in Setogawa-chō, [[:en:Owariasahi|Owariasahi, Aichi]], Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yamano-kami-chō, [[:en:Handa, Aichi|Handa, Aichi]], Aichi Prefecture. Written as "Yama no Jinja" (山之神社). * Located in Tenno-chō, Handa, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yanabehigashimachi, Handa, Aichi Prefecture. * Located in Yama no Kami, [[:en:Taketoyo|Taketoyo, Aichi]], Chita District, Aichi Prefecture. Written as "Yama no Jinja" (山ノ神社).
In the Tōkai region, most of these are small shrines, but there are a large number overall, especially when including shrine precinct shrines.
